title: Spacious 2 Bedroom Flat with Parking!
posting_body: ['Spacious, bright, Inner Sunset 2 bedroom in a 2 unit building with parking!', 'This beautiful 2 bedroom, 1 bath apartment, a block from Irving Street and a', 'stone’s throw from Golden Gate Park, features a recently renovated kitchen and bath and', 'refinished wood floors.', 'Enjoy cooking in this delightful kitchen with laminated wood', 'flooring, quartz countertops, generous cabinets, range and a large', 'pantry.', 'The kitchen flows into a spacious eating area with plenty of natural light.', 'The thoughtfully remodeled bathroom has beautiful tile work', 'with separate tub and shower, tile floor, and vanity.', 'The spacious bedrooms, one with a balcony overlooking the garden and the other with a view of the', 'garden, have ample closet space, and an additional hall linen closet provides extra storage.', 'The unit also comes with shared garage parking and shared garden.', 'This classic 1938 building will charm you with beautiful character and', 'modern touches.', 'Located one block from the Irving', 'Street shopping/restaurant corridor.', 'Buses and the N Judah line are', 'close by.', 'Features:', '2 bedroom /1', 'remodeled bathroom', 'Remodeled kitchen', 'Dining area', 'Wonderful natural light', 'Hardwood floors', 'Garage Parking', 'Shared washer and dryer in garage', 'Terms:', 'Rent $3,700.00 per month', 'Security $5,550.00 (month and ½)', 'Must have good credit', '1 year lease', 'No pets', 'No smoking']
